items.title: Awesome Datascience
items.content_text:
### Tutorials

*   [#tidytuesday (⭐7.5k)](https://github.com/rfordatascience/tidytuesday) A weekly data project aimed at the R ecosystem.
*   [Data science your way (⭐608)](https://github.com/jadianes/data-science-your-way)
*   [PySpark Cheatsheet (⭐571)](https://github.com/kevinschaich/pyspark-cheatsheet)

*   [Tutorials of source code from the book Genetic Algorithms with Python by Clinton Sheppard (⭐1.2k)](https://github.com/handcraftsman/GeneticAlgorithmsWithPython)

*   [Python for Data Science: A Beginner’s Guide](https://learntocodewith.me/posts/python-for-data-science/)
*   [Minimum Viable Study Plan for Machine Learning Interviews (⭐11k)](https://github.com/khangich/machine-learning-interview)
*   [Understand and Know Machine Learning Engineering by Building Solid Projects](http://mlzoomcamp.com/)

items.title: Awesome Vehicle Security
items.content_text:
### Presentations

*   [Remote Exploitation of Honda Cars](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y4Uzm-CTa0I\&ab_channel=CarHackingVillage) - The Honda Connect app used by Honda City 5th generation used weak security mechanisms in its APIs for access control which would allow a malicious user to perform actions like starting the car, locking/unlocking car etc. remotely by interacting with it's Telematics Control Unit (TCU)
items.content_html:
Presentations

  • Remote Exploitation of Honda Cars - The Honda Connect app used by Honda City 5th generation used weak security mechanisms in its APIs for access control which would allow a malicious user to perform actions like starting the car, locking/unlocking car etc. remotely by interacting with it's Telematics Control Unit (TCU)

items.title: Awesome Zsh Plugins
items.content_text:
### Plugins / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [fd (⭐8)](https://github.com/aubreypwd/zsh-plugin-fd) - Use [fzf (⭐72k)](https://github.com/junegunn/fzf) to browse directories.
*   [plenv (⭐1)](https://github.com/TwoPizza9621536/zsh-plenv) - Plugin for the perl [plenv (⭐524)](https://github.com/tokuhirom/plenv) version manager based on jenv.
*   [pyenv (twopizza9621536) (⭐0)](https://github.com/TwoPizza9621536/zsh-pyenv) - Based on the oh-my-zsh [pyenv (⭐180k)](https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/tree/master/plugins/pyenv) plugin with modifications from the rbenv and jenv plugins.

### App Releases / Board

*   [Chinese Checkers](https://www.dong.digital/chinesecheckers/) - [Android](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=digital.dong.chinesecheckers), [iOS](https://apps.apple.com/app/chinesecheckers/id1596651307) - Play Chinese Checkers (Sternhalma), a popular strategy board game, online with friends/strangers or offline with bots. By [Dong Digital](https://www.dong.digital "Dong Digital").
